Christopher Egan https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Christopher_Egan 0 Christopher Andrew Egan (born 29 June 1986) is an Australian actor. He played Nick Smith in the Australian soap opera Home and Away from 2000 to 2003, and David Shepherd on the NBC television drama Kings. He also portrayed Alex Lannon in the Apocalyptic TV series, Dominion. Christopher_Andrew_Egan ( born_29_June_1986 ) is an_Australian_actor .
